text: Tulus Widodo Kalimanto (born 23 August 1965) is an Indonesian former cyclist. He competed in the men's sprint at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Indonesia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
